approach :- binary search

-> phele first element find krne ke liye binary-search uske baad last-element ke liye

// for first position

search target-element using binary search & jb element match ho jaye to use (mid) arr[0] m store kra do
-> uske baad check kro ki mid ke left side m same elements h kya (right = mid-1) yadi h to arr[0] m vo mid-index store krte jao jb tk "left > right" na ho jaye


// for last position

same binary-search process & jb element match ho jaye to use arr[1] m store kra do
uske baad check kro ki mid ke right side m same elements h kya (left = mid-+1) yadi h to arr[1] m vo mid-index store krte jao
